dct_title_s: Plan of the town of Waterford
dct_description_sm: Photostats of original manuscript map done approximately 1795 located in the Pennsylvania State Archives.; Includes legend.; Alternate title: A correct Plan of the Town of Waterford and out-lots.; Relief shown by shading.
